{"tid":690837,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中學和本地大學，應否被淘汰取代","createTime":"2018-06-05T07:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T10:53:46.000Z","uid":149978,"like":8,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"27129fa43e91c2deb8cbe9b495655163b3608975","tid":690837,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T07:40:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.coursera.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coursera.org%2F&d=0XhAkqkgYuNAEGTiFswEk3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=3937e8ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.coursera.org/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edx.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edx.org&d=0XhAkqkgYuNAEGTiFswEk3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=551391f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edx.org</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://executive.mit.edu/openenrollment\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexecutive.mit.edu%2Fopenenrollment&d=0XhAkqkgYuNAEGTiFswEk3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=73a46be9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://executive.mit.edu/openenrollment</a><br />\n<br />\n現在網上，開始越來越多舉辦，大規模的公開網上證書/文憑/學位課程。<br />\n<br />\n類似coursera, edx 或mit的行政學院，佢地會邀請頂尖大學，在呢些網上平台任教，學生完左可以參加考試拿證書。<br />\n<br />\n雖然網上教學一向都存在。<br />\n<br />\n但當世界頂尖大學（eg哈佛、MIT、Stanford、Oxford、Princeton，也有清華北大、東京大學等）和世界頂尖企業（Microsoft, google）都參與和支持。<br />\n<br />\n仲有些大學緊online degree course, online master degree course。<br />\n<br />\n開始證明，獲優質的教育，係網上，比現實課堂教學，又平又好又優質，又冇咁多教畜和垃圾hea老師。<br />\n<br />\n其實將來（甚至現在），中學和本地較弱的大學，仲有冇存在的必要？"},{"pid":"6118dab63eec15b675542cd64bbc7f5b3d1830ed","tid":690837,"uid":125168,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T07:51:56.000Z","msg":"中學個個年紀冇人逼你讀，有幾多人會自己肯自修讀書"},{"pid":"19b1257204a11e609d8229b0eac7297dfa89cbb2","tid":690837,"uid":149978,"like":4,"dislike":29,"score":-25,"quote":{"pid":"6118dab63eec15b675542cd64bbc7f5b3d1830ed","tid":690837,"uid":125168,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T07:51:56.000Z","msg":"中學個個年紀冇人逼你讀，有幾多人會自己肯自修讀書"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T08:07:29.000Z","msg":"此言差矣<br />\n唔想讀書的中學生<br />\n被逼入中學讀書<br />\n先搞搞陣<br />\neg 少則上堂傾計嘈住，create 一個非學習氣氛。中則玩校園欺凌，排擠。大則係學校搞事（食煙吸毒）。"},{"pid":"5d2a258f463e40a0a0ff4b73bb24c1e6c4b2984a","tid":690837,"uid":180156,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T08:28:48.000Z","msg":"中學係提供一個地方比人玩<br />\n而唔係學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0f4ce2e6c0e6fbcdd90a66eb294a50141c3f6d","tid":690837,"uid":87745,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"5d2a258f463e40a0a0ff4b73bb24c1e6c4b2984a","tid":690837,"uid":180156,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T08:28:48.000Z","msg":"中學係提供一個地方比人玩<br />\n而唔係學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T09:01:01.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n學校其中一個最重要既用處係比人學點同人相處<br />\n什至去到大學一大班人讀書你識到既朋友建立到既人脈都係同冇讀過大學既人差好遠"},{"pid":"2106dfc1c9491998d9d040123a9b41a9d57b7006","tid":690837,"uid":86587,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T09:08:17.000Z","msg":"仲以為係烏大龜開post添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489968a93e37636bfcd62907171c3f334ca08758","tid":690837,"uid":134907,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2106dfc1c9491998d9d040123a9b41a9d57b7006","tid":690837,"uid":86587,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T09:08:17.000Z","msg":"仲以為係烏大龜開post添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T09:19:00.000Z","msg":"其實佢分身黎<br />\n唔好踢爆佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997dc0553357f37792f48582df38121101c4e98f","tid":690837,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9